px">                                Cancellation Policy</a><br />                        <br />                        <b>THIS IS AN AUTOMATED MESSAGE</b> - PLEASE DO NOT REPLY DIRECTLY TO THIS EMAIL.                        IF YOU WISH TO CONTACT HEALTHFAIR VIA EMAIL PLEASE USE <a href="mailto:INFO@HEALTHFAIR.COM">                            INFO@HEALTHFAIR.COM</a>                    </td>                </tr>            </table>        </td>    </tr></table>'
